title: Windjammer cross-country's 'Race for the Trail' Oct. 10
text:
Windjammer cross-country's 'Race for the Trail' Oct. 10 Event is part of school's homecoming festivities By Staff | Oct 09, 2015 
Rockport â€” The Camden Hills Regional High School cross-country team will host a 5-kilometer race on Saturday, Oct. 10 at 8:30 a.m. 
Registration begins at 7 a.m. The event, open to those of all ages, is part of the school's homecoming festivities. 
The event will raise money to help develop a new 5K course on the school campus. 
For more information, call coach Helen Bonzi at 207-236-3384 or email her hbonzi@mac.com. 
Courier Publications' sports staff can be reached by email at sports@villagesoup.com or by phone at 594-4401.
